reviewText: Thought this was a movie about witches, (I don't know what I was thinking). So I didn't even watch it, it can be very well good if this is what you want to watch,

To study Wicca and the Craft we must remember those who went before.  This DVD gives some insight into why witchs have learned to be cautious with whom and how much we share with others who are not true seekers of the Knowledge.
